To share Reserved Instances between accounts in AWS Organizations, you can use the Reserved Instances Exchange feature. The Reserved Instances Exchange allows you to sell or buy Reserved Instances from other accounts in your organization. This can help you to optimize your Reserved Instances usage and save money.



