Amazon RDS is a managed database service that provides a reliable and scalable environment for deploying relational databases. It offers a variety of database engines, including MySQL, PostgreSQL, and Oracle. RDS can be used to store data that changes frequently, but it is not as well-suited for this purpose as EFS.

knowledge:
