A pharmaceutical company operates its infrastructure in a single AWS Region. The company has thousands of VPCs in a various AWS accounts that it wants to interconnect.
Which AWS service or feature should the company use to help simplify management and reduce operational costs?

AWS Transit Gateway
AWS Transit Gateway is a managed service that allows you to connect your VPCs in a single Region. It provides a central hub for routing traffic between your VPCs, which can help to simplify management and reduce operational costs.

Knowledge:
why not VPC peering?
VPC peering is a way to connect two VPCs in the same Region. It is a good option if you only need to connect a few VPCs. However, it can become complex to manage and troubleshoot if you have a large number of VPCs.

AWS Direct Connect is a service that allows you to connect your on-premises network to AWS. It is a good option if you need to connect your VPCs to your on-premises network. However, it can be more expensive than using AWS Transit Gateway.

VPC endpoints are a way to connect your VPCs to AWS services without using the public internet. They are a good option for connecting your VPCs to services that do not support VPC peering. However, they can be more complex to configure than using AWS Transit Gateway.
==================
A company is planning an infrastructure deployment to the AWS Cloud. Before the deployment, the company wants a cost estimate for running the infrastructure.
Which AWS service or feature can provide this information?

AWS Pricing Calculator.
The AWS Pricing Calculator is a tool that can help you estimate the cost of running your infrastructure on AWS. It allows you to select the AWS services that you need and to specify the configuration of those services. The calculator will then generate an estimate of the cost of running your infrastructure.

Knowledge:
Cost Explorer is a tool that can help you track your AWS costs over time. It can help you to identify areas where you can reduce your costs.
AWS Trusted Advisor is a service that can help you improve the security and performance of your AWS infrastructure. It does not provide cost estimates.
AWS Cost and Usage Report is a report that provides you with detailed information about your AWS costs. It does not provide cost estimates.
