Developer: Developer support is a paid support plan that provides access to technical support via phone, email, and chat. It also includes access to some additional resources, such as knowledge bases and whitepapers.
Business: Business support is a paid support plan that provides access to technical support and additional resources, such as proactive support and account management.
Enterprise: Enterprise support is a paid support plan that provides the highest level of support, including 24/7 access to technical support and a dedicated account team.
==================
