Which of the following are economic advantages of the AWS Cloud? (Choose two.)
Simplified total cost of ownership (TCO) accounting
Faster product launches

Simplified total cost of ownership (TCO) accounting

AWS offers a variety of pricing options, such as pay-as-you-go, reserved instances, and spot instances. This allows you to choose the pricing option that best meets your needs and budget. AWS also offers a variety of tools and services to help you track and manage your costs, such as Cost Explorer and Budgets.

Faster product launches

AWS offers a wide range of services that can help you to launch new products and services faster. For example, you can use AWS to deploy your application in multiple regions with a single click. You can also use AWS to scale your application up or down as needed.
