| Enterprise | 24/7 technical support, priority access to support engineers, case management, pro-active support, access to APN, business relationship manager, technical account manager |

| Plan | Response time |
|---|---|---|
| Basic | Business hours |
| Developer | 12 hours |
| Business | 1 hour |
| Enterprise | 15 minutes |

